name: Visible Thoughts: 017
description:
017 of the Visible Thoughts series.

I wish weddings weren't so expensive. I wish governments didn't capitalize on something as abstract and complex as love. But then again, maybe it's a good thing. I thought I wanted this beautiful, opulent wedding where all my 100+ family could attend, but nothing could replicate the vision I had without spending money that could buy a car, or be put toward a house. Then we decided to just do it in the backyard with only my closest friends and family - those who know me more than myself. And that feels right.
